
/*
 * This Hyperlambda code snippet adds nodes to the current context by invoking the [add] slot. It retrieves nodes from a specified path using [get-nodes] and adds them as children to the node referenced by the expression in [add]. The [get-nodes] slot targets nodes under [.arguments] at the path [params]. 
 * 
 * 1. [add] - Adds nodes to the current context.
 * 2. [get-nodes] - Retrieves nodes from the specified path [.arguments/*/params/*].
 */
add:x:./*/invoke
   get-nodes:x:@.arguments/*/params/*
